<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dinkelsbühl</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Ausstellung einer Urkunde über die Ausrichtung der Streitsache des Ulrich Üllein, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_451" id="224v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l6">Der Stat cʒu Dinckelſpühell </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt vlrich v̈llein vnſer Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l8">vvie Jm der ſache darümb Er vormals etlich dy ewrn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">her gen <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></del> auff das lantgeriht 
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒu </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_451_line_1577284622891_8811">her gen </ab></add> <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l14">geladen het / ein auſʒſpruch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_451_line_1577284624670_8816">bey ew </ab></add> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ . 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Vnd </del> des Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l15">ein ſchrift vnd vrkunde begere . vvie das <expan>auſʒgeſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l18">worden 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſeẏ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_451_line_1577284675986_8884">daʒ Er ſich daranach </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_line_1577284677612_8889">vveſt cʒu richten </ab></add> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jm </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l16">Jm </ab></add> des alſo <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l21">
<add><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l19">ein ſchrift vnd vrkunde ſchıken wöllet </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> tun wöllet / daʒ ſich der vnſer darnach wiſʒ cʒe </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_451_r1l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">rihten </del> . das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> penthecoſ </ab>
</del><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l23"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> . Als vvir vormals von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> bete vvegen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> von der </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l24">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> hie vnd klag hıe die Er auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantgeriht cʒu </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> getan hat gevveiſet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> . den <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vllein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l26">burger von der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd klag / dıe Er auf dem lant </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l27">geriht cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> anfangen het / gevveıſet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Alſo </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l28">hat vns <expan>derſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht . vvie daʒ v̈mb </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l29"> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache ein auſʒſpruch vnd teyding bey euch </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l30"><expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ / des Er wol vrkunde bedürff / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_r1l31">des dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . vnter <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> Jnſigel ein ſchrift </ab><ab facs="#facs_451_line_1577284657047_8864">vnd vrkund <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_451" id="224v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Dinckelspühell</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Ulrich Üllein, unser
                            burger, wie im der sache darümb er vormals etlich dy ewrn auff das
                            lantgeriht <add>her gen</add>
<expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geladen het ein auszspruch <add>bey
                                ew</add>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey, des er ein schrift und urkunde
                            begere, wie das <expan>auszgesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey worden,
                                <add>daz er sich daranach west czu richten</add>.
                                    <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <add>im</add> des also
                                    <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen <add>ein schrift und urkunde
                                schiken wöllet</add>. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                            penthecos.</del>
<expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir vormals von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> bete wegen den
                            <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ullein, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        burger, von der <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und klag, die er auf dem
                        lantgeriht czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> anfangen het, geweiset
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also hat uns
                            <expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht, wie daz ümb
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache ein auszspruch und teyding
                        bey euch <expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey, des er wol urkunde bedürff.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir des dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> unter <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> insigel
                        ein schrift und urkund <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
